{
  "stem": "19352.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had the idea that the Jews cannot fight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When the-- the independent day in-- in May in 1948 in Poland, it was the communist country, communist government.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They try-- they helped the Jews in Israel to became a independent country in the beginning, the Russians.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They thought that the Jews are going to be communist, and they're going to have another-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] another country to aggravate the rest of the-- of the world, especially the Americans and the-- and the European free countries.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so-- but the Jews didn't want to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They want to-- they know a lot of the Jews who belonged to [INAUDIBLE] Israel, the-- the parliament there, that they were in Russia, and they were the same thing-- very bad treated there.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they-- they didn't say that you Jewish, but they were treated like-- like the worst kind, like-- like Hitler.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was in May in 1939.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in September 1, I supposed to go to Warsaw, and to be accepted to the dental school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But September 1, they started bombing our city, and I didn't go.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I stayed home for the two, three months, how--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, because a-- a few days-- a few weeks before the invasion of Poland, Chamberlain and-- and Daladier from France-- and Chamberlain from England-- they came back from a convention-- a conference with Hitler.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they had a written statement that they will-- he's not-- he doesn't want a war.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He doesn't want anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the only thing he wants, he wants Sudetendeutschland, to take a piece of-- of-- piece of Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then he's not going anywhere.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's-- I was-- I-- I took a bath.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I was in my robe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they started bombing.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
